<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When using the findManyToManyRowset on Zend_Db_Table_Row all the Rows returned are populated with data but not marked as stored. As a result when performing a save using $row-&gt;save() it tries to add a new record instead of updating the existing record.</p>

    </div>
</div>

